1.Open eclipse ide
2.Launch the eclipse in the desired location
3.In the menu bar, File->New->Java project
4.Give a title to your project and create project
5.Right click on your folder and create new package
6.Right click on the package and create a new class and give it a name(Camel case) and write your code
7. Go to the location where the project folder is located and create a new text document and give it a name as "sample_input"
8.Paste the input consisting of goodies and prices
9. create another text document and name it as "sample_output"
10.Run your code
11. On giving the number of employees ,the output gets stored in the sample_output text document
